	\, A-skips\n• Main set (25 min) — Intervals or steady tempo — see weekly f
	ocus\n• Strides / accelerations (10 min) — 4–6 short bursts with full walk
	-back recovery\n• Cooldown (5 min) — Easy jog or walk\, stretch calves and
	 hips\n\nInstagram drill library: add links in instagram_drill_library.jso
	n or session_themes.json → running.instagramUrls\n\nTheme focus: aerobic b
	ase\, intervals\, tempo runs\, recovery pace\, soccer-specific conditionin
	g
